hereby ossifying all the league=E2=80=99s restrictions on Fox=E2=80=99s $37=
=2E5 million rookie broadcaster. As loy=
al readers of The Varsity know by hear=
t, Brady won=E2=80=99t be able to make negative comments about officials or=
